title: EYL #192 Don Cannon on Tech, Entertainment & Signing Lil Uzi Vert & Jack Harlow
itunes:title: EYL #192 Don Cannon on Tech, Entertainment & Signing Lil Uzi Vert & Jack Harlow
description:
In episode 192, we sat down with the legendary Don Cannon. Don is the man behind the men. He's the co-founder of Generation Now, the record label for Lil Uzi Vert and Jack Harlow. He's also the co-founder of the TmrO app which is a groundbreaking app designed for artists to find resources through a global online network. 

We discussed the music business, the future of tech in entertainment, his app, and more. #TmrO #music #tech 

EYL University: https://www.eyluniversity.com
